{"tid":2418343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共班狗最撚叻，就係斷章取義","createTime":"2021-02-22T13:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T14:29:34.000Z","uid":153600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e36fbc8b7ebbf337d3fed1c81d80dca2bb499300","tid":2418343,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:54:04.000Z","msg":"【紅線如何劃？】新聞工作者林妙茵︰//夏寶龍文中引用鄧小平的愛國者論述：「愛國者的標準是，尊重自己民族，誠心誠意擁護祖國恢復行使對香港的主權，不損害香港的繁榮和穩定」，夏只說了一半，事實上，鄧小平緊接還有這句：「只要具備這些條件，不管他們相信資本主義，還是相信封建主義，甚至相信奴隸主義，都是愛國者。我們不要求他們都贊成中國的社會主義制度，只要求他們愛祖國，愛香港。」<br />\n<br />\n鄧小平沒有說反對共產黨就不是愛國者，甚至沒有要求愛國者贊成中國的社會主義制度。我好想向夏寶龍主任請教一下，為何只引前半、沒引後半？後半句又該如何理解？//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38401/%E5%A4%8F%E5%AF%B6%E9%BE%8D-%E9%84%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%B3-%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6-38401/%E5%A4%8F%E5%AF%B6%E9%BE%8D%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%84%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%B3%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E8%80%85%E8%AB%96%E8%BF%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F38401%2F%25E5%25A4%258F%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E9%25BE%258D-%25E9%2584%25A7%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6-38401%2F%25E5%25A4%258F%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E9%25BE%258D%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25BC%2595%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2584%25A7%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25AB%2596%25E8%25BF%25B0&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=e9ab2735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38401/%E5%A4%8F%E5%AF%B6%E9%BE%8D-%E9%84%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%B3-%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6-38401/%E5%A4%8F%E5%AF%B6%E9%BE%8D%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%84%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%B3%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E8%80%85%E8%AB%96%E8%BF%B0</a>"},{"pid":"8b95bff40d916b628d59456ee6b4f1c0d310c786","tid":2418343,"uid":366655,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"